{"tid":2209804,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"共派校長：交通工具風險高 鼓勵學生做行路撚 舊屎山竹都係咁啦","createTime":"2020-09-20T02:03:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-20T02:18:21.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6d73ccb87d9a78203bff4ec92841c2078ce98546","tid":2209804,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T02:03:06.000Z","msg":"有中學校長建議鼓勵學生盡量步行上學減人群聚集 <br />\n<br />\n中小學及幼稚園學生將於星期三起分階段回校上課，津貼中學議會當然執委林日豐在本台節目表示，各學校衛生情況理想，但擔心學生乘坐交通工具回校時有感染風險，認為可鼓勵步行路程在45分鐘內的學生，行路上學，減少人群聚集之餘可增強體魄。 <br />\n<br />\n資助小學校長會名譽主席張勇邦就認為，最重要是與家長溝通，舉例指小六學生12月初已要考呈分試，學校可向家長保證，考試範圍只會包括面授課堂內容，讓家長覺得公平；而他任職的學校，明日和後日會安排小一學生回校體驗校園生活。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2358037\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2358037&d=1nW%2FAbATR%2BcU2iH%2BEMdxE2WzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=e927d716\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2358037</a>"},{"pid":"715988fd714d5587c5301b339f2649b60c9f7712","tid":2209804,"uid":330227,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T02:06:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好<br />\n不過校長你行咗先<br />\n記住咩埋學生個書包"},{"pid":"99ee3e3929e36b3a016a1b9e6ad235c4deeea88d","tid":2209804,"uid":54721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"715988fd714d5587c5301b339f2649b60c9f7712","tid":2209804,"uid":330227,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T02:06:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好<br />\n不過校長你行咗先<br />\n記住咩埋學生個書包"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T02:08:56.000Z","msg":"著埋件校褸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\